        "content": "<p>I gave a mini <code>divp</code> challenge to a new user at <a class=\"stream-topic\" data-stream-id=\"113488\" href=\"/#narrow/channel/113488-general/topic/Division.20by.20zero.3B.20integrating.20non-integrable.20functions/with/561956519\">#general &gt; Division by zero; integrating non-integrable functions</a>, which caused me to ask myself if we should have this:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Mathlib</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Tactic</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">NormNum</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Mathlib</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Tactic</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">OfNat</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">instance</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">R</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">DivisionSemiring</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">R</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">CharZero</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">R</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℕ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">hn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">NeZero</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>